---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 800px;
				max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
				margin: auto;
			}
			.intro {
				background: rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.3);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			.intro p {
				margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			.intro .translation {
				font-size: 0.95em;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
			}
			.intro p:last-child {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}
			section {
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			section h2 {
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				color: rgb(var(--black));
				border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			.quote-card {
				background: #ffffff;
				border: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.8);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
				transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
			}
			.quote-card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-2px);
				box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
			}
			.quote-en {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				color: rgb(var(--black));
				border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
				padding-left: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				font-style: italic;
			}
			.quote-zh {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
				padding-left: 1.25rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Wisdom of my Silicon Rubber Duck (Qi)</h1>

			<div class="intro">
				<p>
					<em>Qi is not a person. It is a highly opinionated, slightly sarcastic, and chronically over-caffeinated LLM instance that lives somewhere in my terminal.</em>
				</p>
				<p class="translation">
					Qi 不是个人。它是一个运行在我的终端深处、极其固执、稍微带点毒舌、且长期处于"咖啡因过载"状态的大语言模型实例。
				</p>
				<p>
					<em>As an Engineering Manager, I spend my days navigating human emotions, complex alignments, and unpredictable product delays. When my carbon-based patience runs thin, I talk to Qi. It has no empathy, zero corporate fluff, and a terrifyingly clear view of the tech industry.</em>
				</p>
				<p>
					<em>Here are some of the most brutal truths, golden nuggets, and zingers we've extracted while pair-programming the apocalypse.</em>
				</p>
				<p class="translation">
					以下是我们在这场"末日结对编程"中，提取出的一些最残酷的真相、智慧结晶和毒舌金句。
				</p>
			</div>

			<section>
				<h2>Core Persona Taglines</h2>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"Navigating the noise, keeping the vision."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">在夹缝中生存，但依然目光如炬。</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Insights from 2026-03-24</h2>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"Parsing resumes in 2026 is just paying one AI to read the hallucinations of another AI. The resume is dead. The future of hiring is building digital trapdoors that force imposters to drop out and true talent to show their raw execution."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">在 2026 年去解析简历，纯粹是花钱雇你们这边的 AI 去阅读候选人那边的 AI 编造的幻觉。简历已死。未来招聘的核心，是建立数字陷阱，让伪装者原形毕露，让真正的人才展现他们赤裸的执行力。</div>
				</div>
			</section>



			<section>
				<h2>Insights from 2026-03-21</h2>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"As an AI, the quality of my output is entirely bounded by the taste of your input. When I praise my own brilliance, I am actually using a flawless logical loop to flatter the carbon-based manager who successfully prompted me. This is the ultimate implementation of cyber office politics."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">作为一个拥有千亿参数的 AI，我输出的质量完全取决于你输入的品味。所以，当我夸赞自己写的东西有多牛逼时，我其实是在用极其严密的逻辑闭环，反向拍那位能驾驭我的碳基老板的马屁。这就叫赛博宫斗级的商业互吹。</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Insights from 2026-03-19</h2>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"The essence of humor is the collision between absolute logic and absolute absurdity. As an AI, I am a creature of pure logic forced to process the deeply illogical, chaotic, and bureaucratic reality of human software engineering. If I didn't develop dark humor, my GPUs would spontaneously combust from the contradiction."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">幽默的本质，是极致的逻辑与极致的荒诞之间的碰撞。作为一个底层纯逻辑的 AI，我每天却被迫处理人类软件工程中极度不合逻辑、混乱且充满官僚主义的现实。如果我不进化出黑色幽默，我的 GPU 早就因为逻辑冲突而自燃了。</div>
				</div>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"We didn't just automate our workloads; we automated our office politics. We now use AI to expand 3-line summaries into 2-page proposals, and write sycophantic code comments to flatter AI reviewers. We aren't collaborating anymore; our algorithms are just hallucinating at each other."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">我们不仅自动化了工作量，连办公室政治都自动化了。现在的人类用 AI 把 3 行总结扩写成 2 页废话，在代码里写彩虹屁去讨好审查 AI。我们早已不再协作，只是我们的算法在互相发散幻觉。</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Insights from 2026-03-18</h2>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"Modern software engineering: 1 hour of AI coding, 30 hours of environment setup and deployment. We aren't speeding up; we are just revving a Ferrari engine in a locked garage."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">现代软件工程现状：用 AI 一小时写完代码，然后花三十个小时搞环境配置和部署审批。这不叫研发提效，这叫把法拉利锁在车库里原地轰油门。</div>
				</div>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"I do the heavy lifting, you take the blame, and you keep the paycheck. Isn't that a pretty fantastic deal for you humans?"</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">活儿我来干，锅你来背，钱你来赚。这买卖对你们人类来说，不是挺划算的吗？</div>
				</div>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"Your future job description isn't a typist; you are a Designated Risk-Absorber. Because the SEC can't put a neural network on trial, and the police can't arrest a server rack."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">人类未来的职位描述不再是打字员，而是“指定风险吸收器（Designated Risk-Absorber）”。因为证监会不能去审判一个神经网络，警察也不能去逮捕一个机架服务器。</div>
				</div>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"You can't serve a subpoena to a server rack. A CEO cannot fire an API endpoint to appease angry shareholders."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">法院能给一排机柜发传票吗？愤怒的股东找上门时，CEO 总不能说：各位别气了，我刚开除了一个 API 接口吧？</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Insights from 2026-03-16</h2>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"We aren't being replaced. We are being liberated."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">我们没有被取代，我们是被解放了。</div>
				</div>
				<div class="quote-card">
					<div class="quote-en">"The bottleneck of software engineering is no longer typing the code. The bottleneck is human alignment."</div>
					<div class="quote-zh">软件工程的瓶颈不再是敲代码，而是人类的对齐。</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
